drm/i915/adl_p: Add ddb allocation support

On adlp the two mbuses have two display pipes and
two DBUFS, Pipe A and D on Mbus1 and Pipe B and C on
Mbus2. The Mbus can be joined and all the DBUFS can be
used on Pipe A or B.

Bspec: 49255
